<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199727>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A – H, Paruzelia. A, P. psyllomorpha, habitus (photograph: I. Malenovsky, MMBC). B, P. rawette, habitus and frons. C, P. sa lo me, habitus (photograph: S. McKamey, USNM). D, P. psyllomorpha, right tegmen. E, P. rawette, right tegmen. F, P. s a l o m e, inverted left tegmen. G, P. r a w e t t e, male genitalia, lateral view. H, P. rawette, pygofer and gonostyli, postero-ventral view. An: anal tube; G: gonostyli; Ph: phallic complex; Py: pygofer. Scale 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/199727/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199728>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Distribution of species of Paruzelia in southeast Asia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/199728/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

